<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='293000' id='t-293000'>So here you have a generation of young women</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='295000' id='t-295000'>who grow up thinking of themselves</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='297000' id='t-297000'>as being more powerful earners</span>
