<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='337000' id='t-337000'>This has been going on for 40 years now.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='339000' id='t-339000'>But this process is affecting men</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='341000' id='t-341000'>very differently than it's affecting women.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='343000' id='t-343000'>You'll see the women in red, and you'll see the men in blue.</span>
