<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='437000' id='t-437000'>If you look at management theory these days,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='439000' id='t-439000'>it used to be that our ideal leader</span>
