<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='445000' id='t-445000'>You would be very hierarchical.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='447000' id='t-447000'>You would tell everyone below you what to do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='449000' id='t-449000'>But that's not what an ideal leader is like now.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='451000' id='t-451000'>If you read management books now,</span>
