<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467000' id='t-467000'>And then on top of that, that's created a kind of cascading effect.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='470000' id='t-470000'>Women enter the workplace at the top,</span>
