<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='479000' id='t-479000'>So that's childcare,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='481000' id='t-481000'>elder care and food preparation.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='483000' id='t-483000'>So those are all the jobs that are growing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='485000' id='t-485000'>and those are jobs that women tend to do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='487000' id='t-487000'>Now one day it might be</span>
