<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='521000' id='t-521000'>Well it turns out that they're just very uncomfortable doing that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='524000' id='t-524000'>They're used to thinking of themselves as providers,</span>
