<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='639000' id='t-639000'>Now you laugh,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='641000' id='t-641000'>but that quote has kind of a sting to it, right?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='643000' id='t-643000'>And I think the reason it has a sting</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='645000' id='t-645000'>is because thousands of years of history</span>
