<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686000' id='t-686000'>and they were not really the providers.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='688000' id='t-688000'>So who were they?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690000' id='t-690000'>And this was very disheartening for them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='692000' id='t-692000'>And what he did was he wrote down on the board</span>
